nce I'm waiting on the port. That feels important! There's also a note that says, \\\"All top-level test classes need to be public,\\\" so I’ll need to keep that in mind. I should ensure there's no compile or runtime issues. Maybe the build report will show if any previous dynamic issues pop up. Let’s see how all this works together!\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_TeTVRE9GxI3BzFsxm6hfKw4P|fc_0151f714b5d7aee80169f50c008f1081a394b496d248c2ac5f", "name": "read", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/ch.qos.reload4j/reload4j/1.2.19/build/reports/dynamic-access/dynamic-access-coverage.json", "limit": 200}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2061, "output": 1604, "cacheRead": 15872, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 19537, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777667046681, "responseId": "resp_0151f714b5d7aee80169f50be7070881a38bc26353640274c7"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_TeTVRE9GxI3BzFsxm6hfKw4P|fc_0151f714b5d7aee80169f50c008f1081a394b496d248c2ac5f", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"classes\" : [ {\n    \"callSites\" : [ {\n      \"covered\" : false,\n      \"frame\" : \"org.apache.log4j.net.SocketHubAppender.append(SocketHubAppender.java:253)\",\n      \"line\" : 253,\n      \"metadataType\" : \"reflection\",\n      \"trackedApi\" : \"java.io.ObjectOutputStream#writeObject(java.lang.Object)\"\n    } ],\n    \"className\" : \"org.apache.log4j.net.SocketHubAppender\",\n    \"coveredCalls\" : 0,\n    \"sourceFile\" : \"SocketHubAppender.java\",\n    \"totalCalls\" : 1\n  }, {\n    \"callSites\" : [ {\n      \"covered\" : false,\n      \"frame\" : \"org.apache.log4j.net.SocketHubAppender$ServerMonitor.sendCachedEvents(SocketHubAppender.java:428)\",\n      \"line\" : 428,\n      \"metadataType\" : \"reflection\",\n      \"trackedApi\" : \"java.io.ObjectOutputStream#writeObject